<button mat-button class="tab" [class.active]="isActive" (click)="onClick()">
  <mat-icon
    *ngIf="svgIconName"
    class="tab-icon"

  <label class="tab-content">{{ label }}</label>

    class="close-icon"

  ></mat-icon>
</button>
